Features
1. Master-Detail Interface

    Displays a list of ice cream entries on the main page.
    Each ice cream entry includes a name and description.
    Users can click on any entry to edit its details in a dedicated form.

2. REST API Integration

    Fetches the list of ice creams from a backend API using REST endpoints.
    Supports creating new ice cream entries and updating existing ones via API calls.

3. Real-Time WebSocket Notifications

    The app listens for real-time updates from the server using WebSockets.
    When new ice cream entries are created or updated, the app receives a notification and updates the list accordingly.